CustomField.description: This field is automatically populated with the origin of this job run, identifying the source or trigger that started the job (e.g., scheduled task, user-initiated action, or test class request). Use this information for reporting to track the job's context and initiation point. Do not modify this field, as it is system-generated and essential for accurate reporting.
